-> Question:-
Receive 1 input fron the user (integer) have to print number of repeating digits
testcase 1: a=2333311
       O/P: 2
testcase 2: a=1111787878953
       O/P: 3

Program:-

a = int(input("Enter any num: "))
b={}
for i in str(a):
    if i not in b:
        b[i]=1
    else:
        b[i]=b[i]+1
d=[i[1] for i in b.items() if i[1]>1]
print(len(d))




